OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA warm and
OL,6,Fsunny evening. Staying largely clear
OL,7,Fovernight, with a low risk of some
OL,8,Fpatchy mist or fog pushing in from
OL,9,FIrish sea coasts. A warm night for
OL,10,Fmost.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FAny early fog clearing to
OL,13,Fleave a hot and sunny day across the
OL,14,Fregion. Light winds and high UV levels
OL,15,Fexpected. A very warm evening and
OL,16,Fnight to come too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
